<h2>
    Gear Setup for Bass Fishing Near Salem
</h2>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Rod</strong>: 6’6” to 7’ medium to medium-heavy spinning or baitcasting
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Reel</strong>: 2000–3000 series spinning or low-profile baitcaster
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Line</strong>: 10–15 lb fluorocarbon or braided line with mono leader
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Must-have tools</strong>: Pliers, polarized sunglasses, tackle tray, net
    </li>
</ul>
